				<p><a href="#" class="btn">GET THE FREE SCHOLARSHIP GUIDE</a></p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="wrapper">
			<div class="text">
				<h2 class="title">Scholarship<span>Essay Guide</span></h2>
				<h3>The complete guide on writing scholarship essays</h3>
				<p>Learn some top do’s and don’ts to craft an essay that will allow you to stand out from the crowd.</p>
				<p><a href="#" class="btn">GET THE FREE ESSAY GUIDE</a></p>
			</div>
